    "name": "PinkPantheress",
    "profile": "Victoria Beverley Walker (born April 18, 2001, in Bath, Somerset, England), known professionally as PinkPantheress, is a singer, songwriter, and producer. She began making music on GarageBand while studying in London and gained attention in 2021 with her debut mixtape [m=2340358], which included the tracks “Just for Me” and “Pain.” In 2022, she won the BBC Sound of 2022 poll and issued the EP [m=3187047]. Her collaboration with [a12211966] on “Boy’s a Liar Pt. 2” reached the top 10 of the Billboard Hot 100. PinkPantheress released her debut album [m=3302317] in 2023, followed by the mixtape [m=3841305] in 2025. Her music incorporates elements of alternative pop, drum and bass, and UK garage.",
